<C>__{theresa}
<P>__{(in italian)}
<D>__{happy birthday, molly.}
<A>__{diana hands molly a card from the table. molly starts to open it. tony luna burst in from another room.}
<C>__{tony luna}
<D>__{molly! pack me a bag! quick! ok? c'mon i'm in a hurry!}
<A>__{molly heads for the stairs, leaving behind the half opened card.}
<C>__{molly}
<D>__{but tony, why...?}
