<D>__{business! c'mon, move. do what i tell you!}
<A>__{molly goes upstairs. diana is pissed.}
<C>__{diana}
<D>__{don't do it, momma! make him pack his own bag.}
<C>__{tony luna}
<D>__{i ain't got time to put up with your bullshit today.}
