<C>__{diana}
<D>__{listen goddammit! it's momma's birthday! she deserves better'n this!}
<A>__{tony sorts through the closet looking for a jacket. gamiani comes in puffing with a clumsily wrapped present under his arm.}
<C>__{gamiani}
<D>__{hey, tony. what's shaking? sorry i'm late. i got stuck on wacker. some spook...}
